Package game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Animation
    A graphic which implements a frame by frame animation drawing.
    CameraObservedObject
    A GameObject that depends on the game camera.
    Character
    This class represents all characters in the game which fight.
    ClickableGraphic
    A graphic with the ability to perform actions when clicked on.
    Entity
    A CameraObservedObject that can move and may be affected by gravity and terrain collision.
    GameObject
    One independent part of the game, bound to a location.
    GameSave
    AbstractMethodError Serializable object meant to store the game state in a save file.
    Graphic
    One graphical component in the game to be drawn in a custom way.
    Hitbox
    A class to handle collisions.
    ImageGraphic
    A graphic which is represented by a still image, as opposed to an animation.
    Main
    The main driver class for the game, also a KeyListener.
    Obstacle
    A class of Terrain that represents obstacles which will damage a Character when touched.
    Player
    A class to represent the player, controlled by the user's input.
    ResourceManager
    A class to be statically called in order to save and load Serializable objects.
    Scene
    This class represents a scene which we can swap to using transitionScene(Scenes)
    Terrain
    A CameraObservedObject which represents terrain that gravitational entities will collide with and stand on.
